'''Hyper-rapture''' was a supposed form of madness acquired from staring into [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] for a prolonged time. The standard procedure for Imperial ships was to opaque the [[Transparisteel/Legends|transparisteel]] slabs while traveling through hyperspace to prevent this.

However, [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] enjoyed staring at the kaleidoscopic and swirling patterns of light, and [[Cronal]] found it soothing to gaze into what he thought of as the emptiness outside the universe.

